      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior appointment reflects a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned designation. A comprehensive inspection will confirm its showroom-fresh integrity and mechanical superiority.",
      "price": 47500.0,
